            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E5%96%9D%E8%B1%86%E6%B5%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E5%96%9D%E8%B1%86%E6%B5%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#哪些人不适合喝豆浆#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B1%86%E6%B5%86%E5%92%8C%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B1%86%E6%B5%86%E5%92%8C%E7%89%9B%E5%A5%B6%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#豆浆和牛奶哪个更好#</span></a> 专家称如果自身消化系统不好，例如有胃炎或消化性溃疡等症状，则不建议喝豆浆。豆浆的膳食纤维有可能会加重胃肠道疾病。有心脑血管疾病的老年人，无论是豆浆还是牛奶都要注意控制饮用量，每天不要超过250ml👇🏻 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>   <a href="http://t.cn/A6N0PkRw" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
